{"tid":2443972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地盤工剛刑滿出獄  再被控非法集結  今認罪再還柙候判","createTime":"2021-03-12T11:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T15:32:32.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"458a0601c06992f7f86b69536099f9f7f8856452","tid":2443972,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"地盤工前年10月在旺角向警方私家車掟雪糕筒刮花泵把，去年9月被裁定刑事毀壞罪成，判囚7個月。剛服刑完畢的他，今於西九龍裁判法院承認兩項非法集結罪，涉及前年8月及去年6月的兩次示威活動。控方庭上播片，顯示被告曾在深水埗警署外集結期間手持大聲公，歌唱「深水埗街坊係乖X過你哋，有薑就衝出嚟捉X我哋」。主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">徐綺薇</span>指需要詳細翻閱控方提供的片段和截圖以及辯方提供的求情信，押後至4月1日判刑，同時索取被告背景報告，被告即時還柙，交由懲教看管。<br />\n<br />\n徐官又謂，無可置疑深水埗案件案情較為嚴重，片段顯示現場環境氣氛已十分緊張，<span class=\"red\">被告使用大聲公說出具挑釁性的話，行為會挑動現場人士的情緒。而且被告當時是在法庭保釋下犯案，屬加刑因素。</span>"},{"pid":"101e79e23129ceca3af46de082ce245030c6bc86","tid":2443972,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/NRQONWHPTBDYZIJO2OKCWSIAWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FNRQONWHPTBDYZIJO2OKCWSIAWA%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=ed201672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FNRQONWHPTBDYZIJO2OKCWSIAWA%2F&h=60407e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/NRQONWHPTBDYZIJO2OKCWSIAWA/</a>"},{"pid":"d4d3f66e8bc93b86f7c36e8c5ca0aabac10c2cb5","tid":2443972,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079140616a16e18ed14d19f2409caa85f7e8ffe4","tid":2443972,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9650209f2841efacd267e2f46524a75f967feb8f","tid":2443972,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike"